<h2 class="heading-large">Friends of Goldstone School Silent Auction</h2>

{% if status.live == 'true' %}

<h3>Roll up for the FrOGS silent auction!</h3>

<p>We have managed to secure some amazing prizes for our silent auction, so have a look and see if you can grab a bargain by placing a bid. All bids will be anonymous, so bid what you can afford and good luck!</p>
<p><strong>But hurry, bids close on 18th April 2023. </strong></p>
<p>As always, all money raised goes towards our amazing school and FrOGS projects to help improve the chances of all pupils. Keep an eye on your inbox to find out if you’ve won.</p>
<p>If you have anything we could add to the prize list, let us know at <a href="mailto:auction@frogsauction.com?subject=Item%20donation">auction@frogsauction.com</a>.</p>
<p>Happy bidding and good luck!</p>

{% else %}

<h3>The FrOGS silent auction has finished!</h3>

<p>Thanks for all your bids, we're working out the winners and will email payment links and collection details very soon.</p>

{% endif %}

<ul class="item_list">
  {%- for lot in auctionLots -%}
    <li class="item_list__item item">
      <div class="item__image-container">
        <p class="item__value">Worth £{{ lot.total_value }}</p>
        <img class="item__image" src="{{lot.image}}" alt="" />
      </div>
      <h3 class="item__title" ><span class="item__number">{{ loop.index }}.</span> {{ lot.lot }}</h3>
      <div class="lot-description">
        <p>{{lot.short_description}}</p>
      </div>
      <a href="lots/{{ lot.lot | slug }}" class="btn">See more{% if status.live == 'true' %} and bid{% endif %}</a>
    </li>
  {%- endfor -%}
</ul>
